  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_8",
    "text": "（1）上表中的中位数m的值为 ,众数n的值 为 ; (2)样本中的平均数估计该校七年级学平均每 学期(按18周计算）上学习的时间； (3)已知该校七年级有200名学，估计每周上学 习时间超过2时的学人数.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08073682147756221,
      0.41743503772003354,
      0.48363707622966884,
      0.5196982397317687
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_9",
    "text": "解题思路 （1）把20个数据从小到大排列，求出最 中间两个数的平均数，即为中位数；出现次数最多的数据 即为众数；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0815206741132667,
      0.5230511316010059,
      0.48206937095825986,
      0.5733445096395641
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_22",
    "text": "【分析数据】根据以上数据，得到以下统计量.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5392906133646874,
      0.5241687622240849,
      0.8512639623750735,
      0.539815590947192
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_10",
    "text": "(2)由样本数据的平均数乘18即可； （3）用总人数乘样本中每周网上学习时间超过2小 时的学生人数所占的比例即可.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0823045267489712,
      0.5761385861972618,
      0.48128551832255534,
      0.6258731489242805
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_23",
    "text": "根据以上信息，回答下列问题：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5400744660003919,
      0.618049734562727,
      0.754066235547717,
      0.632578932662755
