    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_11",
    "text": "解析(1)2.5;2.5.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1128747795414462,
      0.6292260407935177,
      0.2461297276112091,
      0.6437552388935457
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_24",
    "text": "(1)表格中的a=_ ,b=_ ;",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5424260239075054,
      0.6359318245319922,
      0.8269645306682344,
      0.6510198379435597
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_12",
    "text": "(2)2.4×18=43.2(小时).",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11444248481285518,
      0.6465493154512434,
      0.28845776993925143,
      0.6605196982397318
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_25",
    "text": "(2)综合上表中的统计量,判断应选购哪台分 装机，并说明理由.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5071526553008034,
      0.6526962838781782,
      0.9077013521457966,
      0.6839899413243923
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_13",
    "text": "答：估计该校七年级学生平均每人一学期（按18周 计算)网上学习的时间为43.2小时.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0823045267489712,
      0.6633137747974295,
      0.48128551832255534,
      0.6962838781782621
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_26",
    "text": "解析（1）把乙组数据按从小到大的顺序排列为 487,490,491,493,498,499,499,499,499,501,501,501, 502,502,502,503,505,505,506,511，位于中间的数是第 501+501 10、11个数，即501,501，则中位数= =501,故a= 2 501；根据已知条件可得出产品合格的范围是490≤x≤ 510,所以甲生产的产品有3袋不合格，故不合格率为{ 20 100%=15%,故b=15%. （6分）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5055849500293945,
      0.6873428331936295,
      0.9077013521457966,
      0.8376641519977648
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_14",
    "text": "(3) 1×200=130(名). $20$",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11444248481285518,
      0.7007544006705784,
      0.27199686458945715,
      0.7275775356244761
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_15",
    "text": "答：每周网上学习时间超过2小时的学生约为 130名.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08073682147756221,
      0.7314892428052528,
      0.48128551832255534,
      0.7644593461860855
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_16",
    "text": "方法总结 求一组数据的平均数、中位数、众数，要严 格按照其定义进计算，特别注意对加权平均数的权的 理解.在求中位数时，一定要先排序，然后再看数据的总个 数是奇数还是偶数.组数据中，平均数和中位数只有 个,而众数可能不一个.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07995296884185774,
      0.7678122380553227,
      0.4828532235939643,
      0.8544286113439509
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_27",
    "text": "(2)工厂应选购乙分装机. (7分）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.538506760728983,
      0.8404582285554624,
      0.9069174995100922,
      0.8549874266554903
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_17",
    "text": "针对训练1（2020河南，17,9分）为发展乡村经济， 某村根据本地特，创办了药粉加厂.该厂需购置 台分装机，计划从商家推荐试的甲、乙两台不同品牌的 分装机中选择.试用时，设定分装的标准质量为每袋 500g，与之相差大于10g为不合格.为检验分装效果，工 对这两台机器分装的成品进了抽样和分析，过程 如下：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08073682147756221,
      0.8572226879016485,
      0.4828532235939643,
      0.9427214305671976
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417_28",
    "text": "理由如下：比较甲、乙两台机器的统计量可知，甲与 乙的平均数相同，中位数相差不大，乙的方差较小，且不 合格率更低.以上分析说明，乙机器的分装合格率更高，且 稳定性更好.所以，乙机器的分装效果更好，工厂应选购乙 机器. （9分）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5071526553008034,
      0.8583403185247276,
      0.9084852047815011,
      0.942162615255658
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1417",
    "order": 29
  }
